        " : سَأَلْتُهُ عَنِ اَلرَّجُلِ يَكُونُ لَهُ اَلدَّيْنُ وَ مَعَهُ رَهْنٌ أَ يَشْتَرِيهِ قَالَ \"نَعَمْ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3837 - Hammad narrated from Al-Halabi, from Abu Abdillah (as), who said:\nI asked Imam (as) about a man who has a debt and holds collateral along with it, can he purchase it?\nImam (as) said: \"Yes.\""
        ]
